<div id="login-guide-banner" class="login-guide" style="display: none;">
    <div class="guide-header">
        <button id="guide-close-btn" class="guide-btn">다시 보지 않기 ✕</button>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-content">
        <div class="guide-text">
            <p>
                1. 카카오로 시작하면 톡과 계정정보 중 선택필요<br />
                2. 계정이 열리면 앱이 로그인되었다면 확인클릭<br />
                3. 앱으로 복귀는 홈화면 앱아이콘 이용<br />
                4. 마이페이지에서 카카오 로그인 확인
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .login-guide {
        position: fixed;
        /* Moved up to 60% to be slightly higher than 65% and avoid button hiding */
        top: 60%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 400px;
        background: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #fee500;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        z-index: 2000;
        padding: 1rem;
        font-family:
            -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .guide-header {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .guide-btn {
        width: 100%;
        background: #fee500;
        color: #191919;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.6rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .guide-btn:active {
        background: #e6cf00;
    }

    .guide-content {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .guide-text p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
        word-break: keep-all;
    }
</style>

<script>
    document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
        const guideBanner = document.getElementById("login-guide-banner");
        const closeBtn = document.getElementById("guide-close-btn");

        // Check if dismissed (Version 3 to force show)
        const isDismissed = localStorage.getItem("login_guide_dismissed_v3");

        const path = window.location.pathname;
        const shoudShow =
            !isDismissed &&
            (path.includes("/login") || path.includes("/mypage"));

        console.log("LoginGuide Debug:", { path, isDismissed, shoudShow });

        if (shoudShow && guideBanner) {
            guideBanner.style.display = "block";
        } else if (guideBanner) {
            guideBanner.style.display = "none";
        }

        closeBtn?.addEventListener("click", () => {
            if (guideBanner) guideBanner.style.display = "none";
            localStorage.setItem("login_guide_dismissed_v3", "true");
        });
    });
</script>
